- Customised learning pathways based on teaching specialisation

**Key Benefits:**
- Reaches educators in remote or under-resourced areas
- Personalises learning despite large enrolment
- Provides data-driven insights for course improvement
- Reduces dropout through targeted support

**Research Evidence:** Attwell & Deitmer (2021) demonstrated that AI-enhanced MOOCs improve completion rates and learning outcomes in VET teacher training.

</div>

### üõ†Ô∏è 3. Hands-On Generative AI Workshops

--{{1}}--
Short, experiential workshops teach educators to use and critically evaluate generative AI tools through practical application.

<div class="activity-box">

**Workshop Structure (Based on Schmitt & Brutzer, 2025):**

**Duration:** 4 hours  
